cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper presents a novel approach to classifier ensemble creation, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The approach is evaluated on high-dimensional biomedical datasets, which suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the use of classifiers and optimization techniques may also indicate a connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
